import React from 'react'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'
import { HeaderWrapper, Logo, LogoPic, Nav, NavItem } from './style'

const Header = () => {
  return (
    <HeaderWrapper>
      <Logo>
        <Link to='/'>
          <LogoPic />
        </Link>
      </Logo>
      <Nav>
        <Link>
          <NavItem>首页</NavItem>
        </Link>
        <Link>
          <NavItem className='current-tab'>社区精选</NavItem>
        </Link>
        <Link>
          <NavItem>业务合作</NavItem>
        </Link>
        <Link>
          <NavItem>新闻中心</NavItem>
        </Link>
        <Link>
          <NavItem>关于我们</NavItem>
        </Link>
        <Link>
          <NavItem>社会责任</NavItem>
        </Link>
        <Link>
          <NavItem>加入我们</NavItem>
        </Link>
      </Nav>
    </HeaderWrapper>
  )
}

export default Header
